		Developed by Greg Smith.

		\n\nPlease send any bug reports, suggestions, constructive criticism or hate mail to
		greg@gregdev.com.au. This is my first attempt at an Android app, and is just a hobby, so please be nice!

		\n\nPlease note that, due to limitations in how posts are downloaded, threads in private forums (In the News, The Pool Room, Feedback, etc.) will open in a browser window rather than within Whirldroid. Private forums will open within Whirldroid, but only \"recent\" threads will be displayed. An Open In Browser menu item is provided so you can easily open the forum in a Web browser to view the remaining threads.
	</string>

